#Mouse Tracking

We tried a variety of mouth-tracking, eye gaze and facial movement tracking softwares with varying results.
Some didn't work well with the distance we were using. Naturally, we didn't want to sit him a half meter away from a big screen tv. We also didn't want a large obtrusive arm reaching out to put the camera on his face.

###The best open source software in our use-case was
     - https://eviacam.crea-si.com/index.php

####Notable software included
     - http://www.cameramouse.org/
     - http://www.inference.org.uk/opengazer/
